191
00:12:35,980 --> 00:12:37,536
A Cẩu ca ca sao thế?

192
00:12:37,560 --> 00:12:38,716
Ta?

193
00:12:38,740 --> 00:12:40,476
Ta tên là Bạch Thái,

194
00:12:40,500 --> 00:12:41,260
